import pyworld as pw
wave_data = wave_data.astype(np.float64) #WORLDfloatfloat
ff, time = pw.dio(wave_data, fs) #
f0 = pw.stonemask(wave_data, ff, time, fs) #
sp = pw.cheaptrick(wave_data, ff, time, fs) #
ap = pw.d4c(wave_data, ff, time, fs) #
